# **Serving a Simple Website with Nginx on Your Personal Domain**

This guide demonstrates how to deploy a **simple HTML website** using the **Nginx web server** on a **Linux virtual machine in Azure**.

---

## **Steps**

### **1. Create and Connect to an Azure Linux VM**
1. Create a **Linux virtual machine** in **Azure**.
2. Connect to your VM using **SSH**:

```bash
ssh <username>@<your-vm-public-ip>
````

---

### **2. Install Nginx**

1. Update package lists:

```bash
sudo apt update
```

2. Install Nginx:

```bash
sudo apt install nginx -y
```

---

### **3. Enable and Start Nginx**

1. Enable Nginx to start automatically:

```bash
sudo systemctl enable nginx
```

2. Start the Nginx service:

```bash
sudo systemctl start nginx
```

3. **Check the Nginx status**:

```bash
systemctl status nginx
```

---

### **4. Create Your Webpage**

1. Navigate to the web root directory:

```bash
cd /var/www/html
```

2. Create an **index.html** file:

```bash
sudo vi index.html
```

3. Paste the following **HTML content**:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DevOps Test Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>ðŸš€ DevOps Deployment Test</h1>
    <p>If you see this page, your deployment worked! âœ…</p>
</body>
</html>
```

---

### **5. Test Your Website**

* Open your browser and navigate to:

```
http://<your-vm-public-ip>
```

* You should see the **DevOps Deployment Test** page. âœ…

---

## **Optional: Map Your Personal Domain**

1. Update your domain **DNS A record** to point to your VM's public IP.
2. Access your website using your domain:

```
http://yourdomain.com
```

---

### âœ… **Result**

You have successfully hosted a **simple HTML website** with **Nginx** on your **Azure Linux VM**.
This method is ideal for **testing deployments** or **learning DevOps basics**.

